## Memory & Disk Management Summary

| Concern | Solution | Impact |
|---|---|---|
| **DeepFace model (~500MB RAM)** | Already loaded once at startup, shared for all verifications. No change needed. | 0 extra memory |
| **Temp files (live frames)** | Already cleaned up in `finally` block. No change needed. | ✓ |
| **Captures (diagnostic JPEGs)** | New `cleanup_old_captures()` deletes files older than 7 days. Runs at startup. | Prevents disk fill |
| **Visitor photos (permanent)** | One photo per visitor, overwritten on each visit. Stored at `visitors/{id}.jpg`. | ~50KB per visitor |
| **Employee photos** | Static — uploaded once by admin. No cleanup needed. | Unchanged |

